✅ TASK 1: Hangman Game

Sample Output (if the word is "apple"):

Welcome to Hangman!
Word: _____
Guess a letter: a
Word: a____
Guess a letter: e
Word: a___e
Guess a letter: p
Word: app_e
Guess a letter: l
Word: apple
Congratulations! You guessed the word.


