✅ TASK 3: Move All .jpg Files

Assume you have:

Folder source/ with files: image1.jpg, image2.jpg, doc.txt

Folder destination/ is empty


Output in terminal:

All .jpg files moved.

Effect:

image1.jpg and image2.jpg moved to destination/

doc.txt remains in source/



